body:
Captain Marvel (who has the appearance of Gamora in this page because Gamora, who has the reality stone, switched her appearance with Carol) communicates with Steve Rogers through morse code to warn him about Gamora being disguised as Captain Marvel.

So badass.

Infinity Wars #2
